***** TEXT CURSOR ***** 
0x3D4->video driver(CRTC) port in vga text mode

Index	Name
0x00	Horizontal Total
0x01	Horizontal Display End
0x02	Horizontal Blank Start
0x03	Horizontal Blank End
0x04	Horizontal Retrace Start
0x05	Horizontal Retrace End
0x06	Vertical Total
0x07	Overflow
0x08	Preset Row Scan
0x09	Maximum Scan Line
0x0A	Cursor Start
0x0B	Cursor End
0x0C	Start Address High
0x0D	Start Address Low
0x0E	Cursor Location High
0x0F	Cursor Location Low